message:
Task finished.

Summary of deliverables:
- /workspace/solution.py — final efficient solution (reads N from stdin, prints the count of integers ≤ N with exactly 9 divisors).
- /workspace/evaluation.txt — evaluation scores and reasoning.
- /workspace/eval_test.py — test harness used for verification (brute-force checks for small N).

Verification performed:
- Sample tests: N=200 -> 3; N=4_000_000_000_000 -> 407073 (matches expected).
- Exhaustive brute-force checks up to N=5000 — all matched.
- Implementation uses a sieve of Eratosthenes up to sqrt(N) and binary search on the prime list; time/memory are suitable for N up to 4e12.

How to run:
- Example: echo 200 | python3 /workspace/solution.py

All work is complete.
